    "isSagsforlobPeriodValid": true,
    "shortName": "BEK nr 9445 af 14/08/2003",
    "documentHtml": "<div class=\"bjelke\">Den fulde tekst</div><DIV CLASS=PARA ID=\"INDHOLD\"> \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<P ALIGN=\"CENTER\" class=\"Titel\" style=\"font-size:16 pt\">  \r\n\r\n Meddelelse om køretøjers indretning og udstyr mv. nr. 1821  \r\n\r\n<BR>  \r\n\r\n Trepunktsseler på alle fremadvendende siddepladser i personbiler  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"lsp8L\">  \r\n\r\n &nbsp;  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"MsoNormal\"  \r\n\r\n style='margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:14.2pt;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left  \r\n\r\n :35.45pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:17.0pt;mso-line-height-rule  \r\n\r\n :exactly'>  \r\n\r\n<B>  \r\n\r\n Detailforskrifter for Køretøjer 2004  \r\n\r\n</SPAN>  \r\n\r\n</B>  \r\n\r\n vil som nærmere angivet  \r\n\r\n nedenfor, indeholde nye bestemmelser, som omfatter krav om trepunktsseler på  \r\n\r\n de  \r\n\r\n midterste siddepladser i personbil M1.  \r\n\r\n</SPAN>  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"MsoNormal\"  \r\n\r\n style='margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:14.2pt;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left  \r\n\r\n :35.45pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:17.0pt;mso-line-height-rule  \r\n\r\n :exactly'>  \r\n\r\n Ændringen  \r\n\r\n sker i forbindelse med implementeringen af Kommissionens direktiv 2000/3/EF  \r\n\r\n og  \r\n\r\n er markeret med en lodret steg i højre margenen.  \r\n\r\n</SPAN>  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"MsoNormal\"  \r\n\r\n style='margin-left:35.45pt;line-height:16.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly  \r\n\r\n ;tab-stops:-63.8pt -2.0cm'>  \r\n\r\n<B>  \r\n\r\n &nbsp;  \r\n\r\n</SPAN>  \r\n\r\n</B>  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"MsoNormal\"  \r\n\r\n style='margin-left:35.45pt;line-height:16.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly  \r\n\r\n ;tab-stops:-63.8pt -2.0cm'>  \r\n\r\n<B>  \r\n\r\n &nbsp;  \r\n\r\n</SPAN>  \r\n\r\n</B>  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n<TABLE class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"  \r\n\r\n  style='margin-left:38.95pt;border-collapse:collapse;mso-table-layout-alt  \r\n\r\n :fixed; mso-padding-alt:0cm 3.5pt 0cm 3.5pt'>  \r\n\r\n<TR>  \r\n\r\n<TD width=\"104\" valign=\"top\" style='width:77.95pt;padding:0cm 3.5pt 0cm  \r\n\r\n 3.5pt'>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"MsoNormal\" style='line-height:16.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;  \r\n\r\n  tab-stops:-63.8pt -2.0cm'>  \r\n\r\n<B>  \r\n\r\n 10.X2.021  \r\n\r\n</B>  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n<TD width=\"496\" valign=\"top\" style='width:372.0pt;padding:0cm 3.5pt 0cm  \r\n\r\n 3.5pt'>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"MsoNormal\" style='line-height:16.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;  \r\n\r\n  tab-stops:-63.8pt -2.0cm'>  \r\n\r\n<B>  \r\n\r\n PERSONBIL M1  \r\n\r\n<SUP>  \r\n\r\n *)  \r\n\r\n</SUP>  \r\n\r\n</B>  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n</TR>  \r\n\r\n<TR>  \r\n\r\n<TD width=\"104\" valign=\"top\" style='width:77.95pt;padding:0cm 3.5pt 0cm  \r\n\r\n 3.5pt'>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"MsoNormal\" style='line-height:17.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;  \r\n\r\n  tab-stops:-63.8pt -2.0cm'>  \r\n\r\n &nbsp;  \r\n\r\n</SPAN>  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n<TD width=\"496\" valign=\"top\" style='width:372.0pt;padding:0cm 3.5pt 0cm  \r\n\r\n 3.5pt'>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"MsoNormal\" style='line-height:17.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;  \r\n\r\n  tab-stops:-63.8pt -2.0cm'>  \r\n\r\n (1)  \r\n\r\n    \r\n\r\n</SPAN>  \r\n\r\n Personbil M1 skal på alle  \r\n\r\n siddepladser på fremad- og bagudvendende sæder, med undtagelse af klapsæder,  \r\n\r\n være forsynet med sikkerhedsseler således:  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n</TR>  \r\n\r\n<TR>  \r\n\r\n<TD width=\"104\" valign=\"top\" style='width:77.95pt;padding:0cm 3.5pt 0cm  \r\n\r\n 3.5pt'>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"parentesbogstav\" align=\"left\"  \r\n\r\n style='margin-left:0cm;text-align:left;  \r\n\r\n  text-indent:0cm;line-height:17.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;tab-stops:  \r\n\r\n  425.2pt'>  \r\n\r\n<IMG BORDER=\"no\" ALT=\"AR718_1.GIF Size: (3 X 147)\" onMouseOver=\"self.status='AR718_1.GIF Size: (3 X 147)'; return true\" SRC=\"/image.aspx?id=22235&img=AR718_1.GIF\">  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n<TD width=\"496\" valign=\"top\" style='width:372.0pt;padding:0cm 3.5pt 0cm  \r\n\r\n 3.5pt'>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"parentesbogstav\" align=\"left\"  \r\n\r\n style='margin-left:0cm;text-align:left;  \r\n\r\n  text-indent:0cm;line-height:17.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;tab-stops:  \r\n\r\n  425.2pt'>  \r\n\r\n a) på fremadvendende  \r\n\r\n sæde: Trepunktssele med dobbeltvirkende inertiretractor (er mærket »Ar4m«,  \r\n\r\n hvor »m« angiver, at retractoren er dobbeltvirkende).  \r\n\r\n</SPAN>  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n</TR>  \r\n\r\n<TR style='mso-yfti-lastrow:yes'>  \r\n\r\n<TD width=\"104\" valign=\"top\" style='width:77.95pt;padding:0cm 3.5pt 0cm  \r\n\r\n 3.5pt'>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"parentesbogstav\" align=\"left\"  \r\n\r\n style='margin-left:0cm;text-align:left;  \r\n\r\n  text-indent:0cm;line-height:17.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;tab-stops:  \r\n\r\n  425.2pt'>  \r\n\r\n &nbsp;  \r\n\r\n</SPAN>  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n<TD width=\"496\" valign=\"top\" style='width:372.0pt;padding:0cm 3.5pt 0cm  \r\n\r\n 3.5pt'>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"parentesbogstav\" align=\"left\"  \r\n\r\n style='margin-left:0cm;text-align:left;  \r\n\r\n  text-indent:0cm;line-height:17.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;tab-stops:  \r\n\r\n  425.2pt'>  \r\n\r\n b) på bagudvendende  \r\n\r\n sæde: Hoftesele evt. med automatisk retractor eller dobbeltvirkende  \r\n\r\n inertiretractor (er mærket »B«, »Br3« eller »Br4m«), eller trepunktssele med  \r\n\r\n dobbeltvirkende inertiretractor.  \r\n\r\n</SPAN>  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n</TR>  \r\n\r\n</TABLE>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"parentesbogstav\" align=\"left\"  \r\n\r\n style='margin-top:3.0pt;margin-right:70.9pt;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left  \r\n\r\n :35.45pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:left;text-indent:0cm;line-height  \r\n\r\n :17.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;tab-stops:425.2pt'>  \r\n\r\n &nbsp;  \r\n\r\n</SPAN>  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n<TABLE class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"  \r\n\r\n  style='margin-left:38.95pt;border-collapse:collapse;mso-table-layout-alt  \r\n\r\n :fixed; mso-padding-alt:0cm 3.5pt 0cm 3.5pt'>  \r\n\r\n<TR>  \r\n\r\n<TD width=\"104\" valign=\"top\" style='width:77.95pt;padding:0cm 3.5pt 0cm  \r\n\r\n 3.5pt'>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"parentesbogstav\" align=\"left\"  \r\n\r\n style='margin-left:0cm;text-align:left;  \r\n\r\n  text-indent:0cm;line-height:17.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;tab-stops:  \r\n\r\n  425.2pt'>  \r\n\r\n &nbsp;  \r\n\r\n</SPAN>  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n<TD width=\"496\" valign=\"top\" style='width:372.0pt;padding:0cm 3.5pt 0cm  \r\n\r\n 3.5pt'>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"MsoNormal\" style='line-height:17.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;  \r\n\r\n  tab-stops:-63.8pt -2.0cm'>  \r\n\r\n (2) Personbil M1 skal ved alle siddepladser på fremad- og  \r\n\r\n bagudvendende sæder, med undtagelse af klapsæder, være forsynet med  \r\n\r\n seleforankringer, der opfylder de konstruktive bestemmelser i  \r\n\r\n</SPAN>  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n</TR>  \r\n\r\n<TR>  \r\n\r\n<TD width=\"104\" valign=\"top\" style='width:77.95pt;padding:0cm 3.5pt 0cm  \r\n\r\n 3.5pt'>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"MsoNormal\" style='line-height:17.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;  \r\n\r\n  tab-stops:-63.8pt -2.0cm'>  \r\n\r\n &nbsp;  \r\n\r\n</SPAN>  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n<TD width=\"496\" valign=\"top\" style='width:372.0pt;padding:0cm 3.5pt 0cm  \r\n\r\n 3.5pt'>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"MsoNormal\" style='line-height:17.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;  \r\n\r\n  tab-stops:-63.8pt -2.0cm'>  \r\n\r\n a) ECE-regulativ nr. 14-04 eller  \r\n\r\n</SPAN>  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n</TR>  \r\n\r\n<TR>  \r\n\r\n<TD width=\"104\" valign=\"top\" style='width:77.95pt;padding:0cm 3.5pt 0cm  \r\n\r\n 3.5pt'>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"MsoNormal\" style='line-height:17.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;  \r\n\r\n  tab-stops:-63.8pt -2.0cm'>  \r\n\r\n &nbsp;  \r\n\r\n</SPAN>  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n<TD width=\"496\" valign=\"top\" style='width:372.0pt;padding:0cm 3.5pt 0cm  \r\n\r\n 3.5pt'>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"MsoNormal\" style='line-height:17.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;  \r\n\r\n  tab-stops:-63.8pt -2.0cm'>  \r\n\r\n b) Rådets direktiv nr. 76/115/EØF, som ændret ved direktiv nr.  \r\n\r\n 96/38/EF.  \r\n\r\n</SPAN>  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n</TR>  \r\n\r\n<TR>  \r\n\r\n<TD width=\"104\" valign=\"top\" style='width:77.95pt;padding:0cm 3.5pt 0cm  \r\n\r\n 3.5pt'>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"MsoNormal\" style='line-height:17.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;  \r\n\r\n  tab-stops:-63.8pt -2.0cm'>  \r\n\r\n &nbsp;  \r\n\r\n</SPAN>  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n<TD width=\"496\" valign=\"top\" style='width:372.0pt;padding:0cm 3.5pt 0cm  \r\n\r\n 3.5pt'>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"MsoNormal\" style='line-height:17.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;  \r\n\r\n  tab-stops:-63.8pt -2.0cm'>  \r\n\r\n Originalmonteret seleforankring kan dog være udført i  \r\n\r\n overensstemmelse med amerikansk standard FMVSS 210.  \r\n\r\n</SPAN>  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n</TR>  \r\n\r\n<TR style='mso-yfti-lastrow:yes'>  \r\n\r\n<TD width=\"104\" valign=\"top\" style='width:77.95pt;padding:0cm 3.5pt 0cm  \r\n\r\n 3.5pt'>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"MsoNormal\" style='line-height:17.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;  \r\n\r\n  tab-stops:-63.8pt -2.0cm'>  \r\n\r\n &nbsp;  \r\n\r\n</SPAN>  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n<TD width=\"496\" valign=\"top\" style='width:372.0pt;padding:0cm 3.5pt 0cm  \r\n\r\n 3.5pt'>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"MsoNormal\" style='line-height:17.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;  \r\n\r\n  tab-stops:-63.8pt -2.0cm'>  \r\n\r\n Seleforankringer til sæde, som er specielt konstrueret til personer  \r\n\r\n med handicap, skal dog alene opfylde bestemmelsen i pkt. 10.02.001 (6).  \r\n\r\n</SPAN>  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n</TD>  \r\n\r\n</TR>  \r\n\r\n</TABLE>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"MsoNormal\"  \r\n\r\n style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:28.3pt;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left  \r\n\r\n :35.45pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;tab-stops:-63.8pt 496.15pt'>  \r\n\r\n<IMG BORDER=\"no\" ALT=\"AR718_2.GIF Size: (3 X 22)\" onMouseOver=\"self.status='AR718_2.GIF Size: (3 X 22)'; return true\" SRC=\"/image.aspx?id=22235&img=AR718_2.GIF\">  \r\n\r\n</SPAN>  \r\n\r\n____________________  \r\n\r\n</SPAN>  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"TabelFod9\" style='text-indent:21.25pt;tab-stops:35.45pt'>  \r\n\r\n *  \r\n\r\n<SUP>  \r\n\r\n )  \r\n\r\n</SUP>  \r\n\r\n Afsnit 10.X2.021 erstatter 10.02.021 den 1. oktober 2004.  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"MsoNormal\"  \r\n\r\n style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left  \r\n\r\n :35.45pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;tab-stops:531.6pt'>  \r\n\r\n &nbsp;  \r\n\r\n</SPAN>  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"MsoNormal\"  \r\n\r\n style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left  \r\n\r\n :35.45pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;tab-stops:531.6pt'>  \r\n\r\n Detailforskrifter for  \r\n\r\n Køretøjer 2004 træder i kraft den 1. april 2004.  \r\n\r\n</SPAN>  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"MsoNormal\"  \r\n\r\n style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left  \r\n\r\n :35.45pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;tab-stops:531.6pt'>  \r\n\r\n &nbsp;  \r\n\r\n</SPAN>  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"MsoNormal\"  \r\n\r\n style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left  \r\n\r\n :35.45pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;tab-stops:531.6pt'>  \r\n\r\n Bestemmelserne i afsnit  \r\n\r\n 10.X2.021 træder dog først i kraft den 1. oktober 2004.  \r\n\r\n</SPAN>  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"MsoNormal\"  \r\n\r\n style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left  \r\n\r\n :35.45pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;tab-stops:531.6pt'>  \r\n\r\n &nbsp;  \r\n\r\n</SPAN>  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n<P class=\"MsoNormal\"  \r\n\r\n style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:1.0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left  \r\n\r\n :35.45pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;tab-stops:531.6pt'>  \r\n\r\n Ethvert køretøj vil dog straks  \r\n\r\n kunne indrettes efter bestemmelserne.  \r\n\r\n</SPAN>  \r\n\r\n</P>  \r\n\r\n<DIV CLASS=GIVET ID=\"GIVET\">  \r\n\r\n<FONT SIZE=\"3\">  \r\n\r\n<P CLASS=GIVET ALIGN=\"CENTER\"><I>Færdselsstyrelsen, den 14. august  \r\n\r\n 2003</I></P>  \r\n\r\n<P CLASS=SIGN1 ALIGN=\"CENTER\">Ib Rasmussen</P>  \r\n\r\n</FONT>  \r\n\r\n</DIV><!-- End of \"GIVET\" -->  \r\n\r\n</DIV>",
